    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior is clean with no scratches, dents, or rust. The interior is pristine \u2014 upholstery, dashboard, and all trim are in excellent shape with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car runs and drives as it should, with all systems functioning properly. A well-maintained vehicle being sold straightforwardly.",
